NEW AP (Accesspoint)
---------------------
    >> sudo nmcli device wifi hotspot ssid [SSID] password [PASSWORD] ifname [INTERFACE]
    >> sudo nmcli device wifi hotspot ssid rasp password 12345678 ifname wlan0

    >> nmcli connection show
    
    //autoconnect
    >> sudo nmcli connection modify [NAME] connection.autoconnect yes
    >> sudo nmcli connection modify Hotspot connection.autoconnect yes

    //set priority 100
    >> sudo nmcli connection modify [NAME] connection.autoconnect-priority 100
    >> sudo nmcli connection modify Hotspot connection.autoconnect-priority 100
